text: Olinda Castielle born Olinda Borggren is a Swedish TV personality who was a contestant on the American reality show Joe Millionaire and the first season of the Swedish version of Paradise Hotel. == TV shows == *Paradise Hotel (Swedish Edition) *Paradise Hotel Extra (season 1 as a guest) *Paradise Hotel Extra (season 2 as a host) *Joe Millionaire *The OP Tour *Little Italy == Other websites == *Olinda and Patrick official web site, Oplounge. *Paradise Hotel - tv4.se *About Olinda on Joe Millionaire - tvrules.net *Little Italy - tv4.se Category:1982 births Category:Living people
